Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The president's nose
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xl95
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Aug 1985
The president's skin cancer removal prompts reminders on the perils of sun bathing. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.